Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:05.65,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Time and time again my hopes are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:11.64,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}It's like a never-ending marathon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.07,0:24:18.28,ed-en,,0,0,1,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I hear voices every night of the ones I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:20.86,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}That I loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.93,0:24:26.37,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I try to find the place where I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.95,0:24:32.86,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Until I do, I guess I'll carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.86,0:24:35.73,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Trapped in every sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.73,0:24:39.25,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Feel like I'm gonna lose my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.25,0:24:42.05,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:54.59,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love, without love, without love...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.73,0:24:59.33,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I played the game of life and had a ball
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.76,0:25:05.37,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Crazy of me to think I had it all
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.45,0:25:12.26,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I kept holdin' on to the power, then lost
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:15.87,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}My freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.39,0:25:24.28,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I guess I have to learn there's no freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:27.22,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Without love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:05.65,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我一次又一次失去希望
