Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚做了个很可怕的梦
